B.Pi=s([B.VG],t.A5)
B.L7=new A.cj("ten_minute_mindfulness_breathing","Ten Minute Mindfulness of Breathing","Energizing 1:1 breathing (3 seconds inhale, 3 seconds exhale) for balanced mood and alertness. This equal ratio promotes balanced sympathetic/parasympathetic activity for positive emotional states.","breathing_practices","assets/sounds/meditation/guided/breathing_practices/Ten Minute Mindfulness of Breathing.mp3",601,"Padraig O'Morain",B.Ps,"This balanced breathing pattern maintains alertness for positive mood without triggering stress responses. The 3-second intervals are sustainable and research-optimal for most people, promoting emotional well-being and cognitive clarity.","You'll feel alert yet calm, with a natural mood lift. This practice is excellent for starting your day or when you need focused, positive energy.",B.Pi,null,null)
